::: {#d62d2ee8 .cell execution_count=3}
``` {.python .cell-code}
taus = {int(y): tr.critical_threshold(tr.percolation_curve(g))
        for y, g in edges.groupby("year") if int(y) <= latest}
ts = pd.Series(taus).sort_index()
px.line(ts, markers=True, title="Critical threshold τ_c by year — the market's cohesion scale",
        labels={"index": "year", "value": "τ_c"}).update_layout(showlegend=False).show()
```

